        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[12px] text-ink-500">
          These are the icons you'll see most across the site — in the top bar, in tree links, beside copyable code, and in callouts. They sit at
          <code class="mono text-[12px]">
            h-3.5 w-3.5
          </code>
          (14px), coloured
          <code class="mono text-[12px]">
            text-ink-500
          </code>
          , paired with body text or a mono label. Larger swatches below are reference at 20px so the stroke geometry is visible.
        </p>
